subject: Happy Birthday!
message: Dear Geralt of Rivia,(new-line)(new-line)Congratulations on your 32nd birthday! I hope this day brings you joy, laughter, and many wonderful memories. May this year be filled with new adventures, success, and happiness. Warm wishes on your special day!(new-line)(new-line)Warm Wishes,(new-line)Matiss
